Whilst doing the QA for CONF-29810 we discovered that

{code}
AJS.$.ajaxSetup()['timeout']
{code}

is undefined on the editor page. If you come from the view page via quick edit (push state) it will be defined with 12s whatsoever, so you'd have to reload the page and then check again. I think it's quite crucial to have a consistent behaviour here as the browser defaults differ (e.g. Chrome/FF seem to have no timeout).

