We use Connectwise as our ticketing system. When an issue is reported and a ticket is opened, the ticket is assigned to an engineer for processing. Since the change over, whenever the NOC updates the ticket or the alarm reoccurs, the ticket is being automatically put back into a "new" status where it has to be reassigned to the technician. We would like for the update process to not change the ticket status but rather just update the notes in the ticket.

